- [ ] **Type** is correct (`feat`, `fix`, `docs`, etc.)
- [ ] **Subject** is under 50 characters
- [ ] **Imperative mood** ("add" not "added")
- [ ] **Specific and clear** description
- [ ] **Scope** included when helpful
- [ ] **No period** at end of subject

