```

#### Format Template
```
<type>(<scope>): <description>

[optional body]

[optional footer]
```

#### Examples
```bash
feat(engine): add antenna optimization algorithm
fix(ui): resolve mobile layout issue
docs: update installation guide
test(core): add simulation accuracy tests
```

